ImprovedMysqlSchemaDumper
=========================

Use mysqldump for rake schema operations.  Necessary when using VIEWS
or other database constructs rails doesn't understand.


Example
=======

Get the code on github:

  http://github.com/smtlaissezfaire/improved_mysql_schema_dumper


Add it to your rails project:

  git submodule add \
      git://github.com/smtlaissezfaire/improved_mysql_schema_dumper.git \
      vendor/plugins/improved_mysql_schema_dumper


The following rake tasks are affected:

  db:schema:dump
  db:schema:load
  db:structure:dump
  db:test:clone_structure


